These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, cooking, card-games, board-games, woodworking
There are 5 different nationalities: american, italian, dutch, argentine, nigerian
5 different pets are kept: rat, pony, mouse, bird, hedgehog
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, cricket, volleyball, badminton, soccer
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the american##1
 4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the owner of the pony is the argentine##1
 6. the italian is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 8. the italian is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the italian##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
11. the owner of the pony is the person who's sport is handball##1
12. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | cooking  | drawing    | board-games | card-games    | woodworking  |
| Nationality   | italian  | american | dutch | argentine | nigerian  |
| Pet           | rat     | hedgehog     | bird  | pony   | mouse    |
| Sport         | volleyball | badminton    | cricket | handball  | soccer |

