.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There 5 different types of food: peas, pumpkin, grapes, lime, orange
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, firefighter, analyst, engineer, teacher
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, disaster, sports, thriller, crime
There are 5 different nationalities: malaysian, pakistani, japanese, indian, canadian
 1. the engineer is on the right of the malaysian##1
 2. the japanese is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the pakistani is on the right of the indian##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 6. the analyst is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 7. the teacher is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 8. the person eating grapes is the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the indian is the person eating grapes##1
10. the person eating pumpkin is in the middle##1
11. the person eating lime is on the left of the japanese##1
12. the person eating grapes is the firefighter##1
13. the person eating orange is on the left of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Food          | grapes        | orange | pumpkin     | lime      | peas  |
| Job           | firefighter   | analyst | teacher    | engineer | designer |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | thriller     | crime | action    | disaster  |
| Nationality   | indian     | pakistani | malaysian    | canadian      | japanese    |

