.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, mirinda
The people have 5 different hobbies: rock-climbing, collecting, singing, gardening, filmmaking
There are 5 different nationalities: pakistani, russian, indonesian, french, chinese
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, tram, bike, bus, motorbike
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the chinese##1
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the pakistani is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1
 5. the indonesian is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 8. the indonesian is on the right of the french##1
 9. the person driving the motorbike is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the bike is on the right of the russian##1
11. the indonesian is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the person drinking almond-milk is the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk          | hot-chocolate  | coffee       | soy-milk     | mirinda      |
| Hobby         | collecting | filmmaking | gardening  | singing   | rock-climbing    |
| Nationality   | russian        | chinese | pakistani | french    | indonesian   |
| Transport     | car   | bike | motorbike      | tram | bus |

