The people prefer 5 different music-genres: soul, classical, r&b, folk, metal
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, airplane, roller, subway
 1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 3. the fan of classical is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the fan of soul is the person watching comedy movies##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 8. the person driving the subway is in the middle##1
 9. the fan of folk is on the left of the person eating corn##1
10. the person eating pomegranate is the fan of r&b##1
11. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
12. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food          | artichoke        | corn       | strawberry | cucumber   | pomegranate  |
| Movie-Genre   | western | animation | fantasy | comedy   | adventure |
| Music-Genre   | folk         | metal     | classical | soul | r&b     |
| Transport     | skateboard        | snowmobile        | subway    | roller    | airplane      |

