 4. the spanish is on the right of the british##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the spanish is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
10. the japanese is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the dog is on the left of the japanese##1
12. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
13. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
14. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
