 8. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 9. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking water##1
11. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is the fan of gospel##1
13. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk      | water       | hot-chocolate         | mirinda  | coffee |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | musical | adventure | comedy  | documentary  |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | metal    | d&b        | pop | salsa     |
| Pet           | goat | lizard      | goldfish       | dog   | rat   |

