.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, romance, drama, time-travel, disaster
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, pop, d&b, reggae, classical
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, cat, lizard, mouse, goldfish
