 2. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
