.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, soy-milk, almond-milk, water
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, reggae, ambient, soul
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, dutch, german, nigerian, russian
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, skateboard, ship, bus, trike
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of ambient is the person driving the airplane##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 4. the fan of dubstep is the russian##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the fan of reggae is the dutch##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
11. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
12. the fan of soul is in the middle##1
13. the australian is the person drinking almond-milk##1
14. the nigerian is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
